sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Web/Android
    participant EF as razorpay-create-order
    participant RZ as Razorpay
    participant WH as razorpay-webhook
    participant DB as PostgreSQL RPC
    U->>EF: JWT + amount_inr
    EF->>RZ: Create order
    EF->>DB: Insert payment_intents
    EF-->>U: order_id, key_id, intent_id
    U->>RZ: Razorpay Checkout SDK
    RZ->>WH: payment.captured webhook
    WH->>DB: confirm_wallet_deposit
    DB->>DB: wallet_history deposit + receipt
    U->>DB: Poll payment_intents status=paid
